'''蓝色群岛航空'''是[[海峡群岛|海峡群岛]]的一家[[航空公司|航空公司]]。公司总部位于[[根西岛|根西岛]][[圣彼得港|圣彼得港]]，注册地则是奥德尼岛[[Saint_Anne,_Alderney|Saint Anne]]。<ref>"http://www.blueislands.com/contact-us {{Wayback|url=http://www.blueislands.com/contact-us |date=20111007062859 }} Contact Us]." Blue Islands. Retrieved on 18 September 2009. "Head Office Our head office is in St. Peter Port, Guernsey, which deals with marketing, PR and media relations and trade enquiries."</ref> 蓝色群岛航空运行海峡群岛内的定期航班以及飞往英国、马恩岛的航班。公司的运营基地是[[泽西岛机场|泽西岛机场]].

